
== Asynchronous processing and the event bus
	<indexterm>
		<primary>Event service</primary>
		<secondary>Asynchronous processing</secondary>
	</indexterm>

	
		Your threads can use the
		`IEventBroker`
		to send event data. Every listener will be automatically called and if
		a method is annotated with the
		`UIEventTopic`
		annotation, it will be
		called in the main thread.
	

	
